'''-{zh-cn:斯蒂芬·巴克利; zh-hk:柏建熙; zh-tw:史提芬·巴克萊;}-'''（{{lang-en|Stephen Barclay}}，{{bd|1972年|5月3日}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.edp24.co.uk/norfolk-life/first_friday_with_steve_barclay_mp_a_website_of_waste_campaign_progress_and_cheering_on_boris_1_1366053 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-11-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130420031837/http://www.edp24.co.uk/norfolk-life/first_friday_with_steve_barclay_mp_a_website_of_waste_campaign_progress_and_cheering_on_boris_1_1366053 |archivedate=2013-04-20 }}</ref>）是一位[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]政治人物，他的黨籍是[[保守黨_(英國)|保守黨]]。

==生平==
自2010年開始，他擔任[[東北劍橋郡_(英國國會選區)|東北劍橋郡]]選區選出的英國下議院議員<ref>{{London Gazette |issue=61230 |date=18 May 2015 |startpage=9120}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Wisbech Standard |url=http://www.wisbech-standard.co.uk/content/wisbech/news/story.aspx?brand=CATOnline&category=NewsWisbech&tBrand=HertsCambsOnline&tCategory=newslatestWIS&itemid=WEED07%20May%202010%2003%3A46%3A36%3A540 |title=3.46AM: Stephen Barclay wins NE Cambs seat and extends Tory majority to more than 16,000 |publisher=Wisbech-standard.co.uk |date= |accessdate=8 May 2010 |archive-date=2020-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329031648/http://www.wisbech-standard.co.uk/content/wisbech/news/story.aspx?brand=CATOnline&category=NewsWisbech&tBrand=HertsCambsOnline&tCategory=newslatestWIS&itemid=WEED07%20May%202010%2003%3A46%3A36%3A540 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他在1994年加入保守黨。2018年11月16日獲委任為[[退出欧洲联盟事务大臣|脫歐事務大臣]]。四日後，宣誓就職[[英國樞密院|樞密院顧問官]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://privycouncil.independent.gov.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/2018-11-20-List-of-Business.pdf|title=BUSINESS TRANSACTED AT THE PRIVY COUNCIL HELD BY THE QUEEN AT BUCKINGHAM PALACE ON 20TH NOVEMBER 2018|date=2018-11-20|language=en|access-date=2018-11-23|archive-date=2020-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200913025149/https://privycouncil.independent.gov.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/2018-11-20-List-of-Business.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年1月31日，[[英國脫歐|英國脫歐]]，[[脫離歐洲聯盟部|脫歐部]]隨之被裁撤，他因而卸任脫歐事務大臣，兩週後改任財政部首席秘書。

